      <title>Tetris - Classic Block Puzzle</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/24/Tetris/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/24/Tetris/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="About-the-Game"><a href="#About-the-Game" class="headerlink" title="About the Game"></a>About the Game</h2><p>The legendary Tetris game, now available as a browser version.<br>Stack falling blocks to complete lines and score points.</p><h2 id="How-to-Play"><a href="#How-to-Play" class="headerlink" title="How to Play"></a>How to Play</h2><ul><li>Left&#x2F;Right arrows: Move blocks</li><li>Up arrow: Rotate blocks</li><li>Down arrow: Speed up fall</li><li>Spacebar: Drop instantly</li></ul><h2 id="Play-Online"><a href="#Play-Online" class="headerlink" title="Play Online"></a>Play Online</h2><p><a href="https://tetris.com/play-tetris">Play Tetris</a></p><h2 id="Open-Source-Info"><a href="#Open-Source-Info" class="headerlink" title="Open Source Info"></a>Open Source Info</h2><ul><li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/jamestan/tetris">https://github.com/jamestan/tetris</a></li><li>License: MIT</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
